{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"8c00omb6sa7uu9w3lhmxbgj","title":"String Conversion","desc":"","updated":1712863891091,"created":1712863873567,"custom":{},"fname":"lang.java.typing.casting.string conversion","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"cs"},"contentHash":"b94fd13419046af6e11095520c203d49","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"lang.java.typing.casting.string conversion","id":"8c00omb6sa7uu9w3lhmxbgj","vaultName":"cs"},"value":"lang.java.lib.classes.wrappers","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":18,"offset":62},"end":{"line":4,"column":52,"offset":96},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"lang.java.lib.classes.wrappers"}},{"from":{"fname":"lang.java.lib.classes.wrappers","id":"rhm2ueynmzepd2gxd9tj0sx","vaultName":"cs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":77,"column":17,"offset":2255},"end":{"line":77,"column":63,"offset":2301},"indent":[]},"value":"lang.java.typing.casting.string conversion"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"n0d2q53xmh48ef3rhrmjmif","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"string-conversion\">String Conversion<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#string-conversion\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Conversion from primitive type to String</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Done through <a href=\"/cs/notes/rhm2ueynmzepd2gxd9tj0sx\">Wrapper Classes</a> which override the toString() method</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Syntax</p>\n<pre><code>```java\nInteger a = 130;\nString s = a.toString();\n```\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Conversion from String to primitive type</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Each wrapper class has a <em>parse</em> method → parseXXX()</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Syntax</p>\n<pre><code>```java\nint a = Integer.parseInt(s);\nbyte b = Byte.parseByte(s);\n\n//Exception\n//Since String is made of chars anyway \n//considering the String is made of a single character\nchar c = s.charAt(0)\n\n```\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>